            </h1>
          </div>
          <div class="w-32 h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-blue-600 to-indigo-500 rounded-full mx-auto mb-8"></div>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-medium">
            Custode della fede e delle tradizioni religiose di Piedelpoggio
          </p>
